  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "51df8d30",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Need-Capacity Mismatch Index\n",
    "The core metric developed in this notebook is a need-capacity mismatch index. The index compares:\n",
    "- mental health burden\n",
    "- treatment infrastructure\n",
    "\n",
    "using standardized z-scores:\n",
    "Mismatch = z(mental health burden) − z(treatment infrastructure)\n",
    "\n",
    "High values indicate places where poor mental health prevalence is high relative to available treatment infrastructure.\n"
   ]
  },
